Computing estimates of the precision-recall curve

MATLAB IMPLEMENTATION

This archive is organized as follows:

/examples - contains a simple example
/matlab   - contains the full code base

For a simple example, make sure both /examples and /matlab are on your MATLAB
path. Then type:
    prc_demo

Literature:
    K.H. Brodersen, C.S. Ong, K.E. Stephan, J.M. Buhmann (2010).
	The binormal assumption on precision-recall curves. In: Proceedings
	of the 20th International Conference on Pattern Recognition (ICPR),
	4263-4266.

